### **Capital Raising Announcement Summary**  
- **Structure**: Accelerated non-renounceable entitlement offer  
- **Total Raising**: Up to ~A$4.492 million  
- **Key Dates**:  
  - **Retail Offer Close**: 5:00 PM (AEST) 10 July 2025  
  - **Allotment & Issue Date**: 17 July 2025  
  - **Expected Trading Start**: 18 July 2025  
- **Access Materials**: Eligible shareholders can access forms & prospectus at [www.computersharecas.com.au/adroffer](http://www.computersharecas.com.au/adroffer).
